"blocks":{"image_adpaCP":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/3_e95e5e59-5765-4726-b2cc-1e8d1dd0caaf.jpg","media_width":50,"media_position":"start","text_position":"place-self-center-start text-start","icon":"none","icon_width":48,"subheading":"","sub_position":"top","title":"Dual-axis Contoured Headrest","heading_tag":"h4","content":"<p>The AutoFull G5 office chair comes with a two-axis adjustable headrest, offering a modern alternative to traditional fixed designs. You can easily adjust the height of the headrest by 2.36 inches, and the main axis provides a tilt range of 70°. This unique design offers optimal support for your neck, accommodating various sitting positions for all-day comfort.<\/p>","link_text":"","link_url":"","background":"#000000","background_inner":"#000000","background_gradient":"","text_color":"#ffffff","text_gradient":"","button_background":"","button_text_color":"","allow_reverse":false}},"image_CcziwR":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/000_-1_11235c1b-30f0-437f-9765-98270631ffa8.jpg","media_width":50,"media_position":"end","text_position":"place-self-center-start text-start","icon":"none","icon_width":48,"subheading":"","sub_position":"top","title":"360° Adjustable Armrests","heading_tag":"h4","content":"<p>The 360° armrests are designed for optimal comfort and support. They feature a 2.56-inch height adjustment, plus 1.57 inches of front and back rotation and a 40° range for left and right movement. You can adjust the armrests up and down by 20°, and they rotate a full 360°, relieving stress on your shoulders and arms. This flexibility makes it easy to switch between tasks like reading, gaming, or working.<\/p>","link_text":"","link_url":"","background":"#000000","background_inner":"#000000","background_gradient":"","text_color":"#ffffff","text_gradient":"","button_background":"","button_text_color":"","allow_reverse":false}},"image_qXAUe4":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/2_9e9caaba-9c49-46d6-a1a0-b7e0b2b27df8.jpg","media_width":50,"media_position":"start","text_position":"place-self-center-start text-start","icon":"none","icon_width":48,"subheading":"","sub_position":"top","title":"6D Contoured Lumbar Support","heading_tag":"h4","content":"<p>Our lumbar support system is fully adjustable, moving 0.79 inches forward and backward and 2.36 inches vertically. The bottom of the lumbar pillow tilts by 15°, ensuring a snug fit that wraps around your lower back. Made from a breathable mesh material, this support reduces pressure on your back, enhancing your sitting experience.<\/p>","link_text":"","link_url":"","background":"#000000","background_inner":"#000000","background_gradient":"","text_color":"#ffffff","text_gradient":"","button_background":"","button_text_color":"","allow_reverse":false}},"image_jGUAWh":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/5_14689157-4252-4b40-9b8f-bc67fa8ce44c.jpg","media_width":50,"media_position":"end","text_position":"place-self-center-start text-start","icon":"none","icon_width":48,"subheading":"","sub_position":"top","title":"Ultimate Comfort and Adaptability","heading_tag":"h4","content":"<p>The AutoFull G5 features a versatile 4D headrest that provides essential neck support. Its breathable mesh fabric promotes airflow and keeps you comfortable, while the robust wired base ensures long-lasting durability. With an integrated footrest and a tilt function that goes up to 140°, you’ll find the perfect angle for relaxation. Plus, the seat height is adjustable from 17.3 inches to 20.7 inches, accommodating users from 4'11\" to 6'4\".<\/p>","link_text":"","link_url":"","background":"#000000","background_inner":"#000000","background_gradient":"","text_color":"#ffffff","text_gradient":"","button_background":"","button_text_color":"","allow_reverse":false}},"image_p9zVrJ":{"type":"image","settings":{"media_width":50,"media_position":"start","text_position":"place-self-center-start text-start","icon":"none","icon_width":48,"subheading":"","sub_position":"top","title":"Pressure-Dispersing Mesh Material","heading_tag":"h4","content":"<p>High-quality elastic materials paired with top-tier elastic weaving technology ensure optimal support and breathability for long gaming sessions. The durable mesh structure evenly distributes body weight, while the flexible design adapts to your movements for enhanced comfort.<\/p>","link_text":"","link_url":"","background":"#000000","background_inner":"#000000","background_gradient":"","text_color":"#ffffff","text_gradient":"","button_background":"","button_text_color":"","allow_reverse":false}}},"block_order":["image_adpaCP","image_CcziwR","image_qXAUe4","image_jGUAWh","image_p9zVrJ"],"settings":{"section_id":"","full_width":false,"alternate_media_position":false,"column_gap":16,"spacing":"small","sec_background":"#f2f2f2","inner_background":"#f2f2f2","padding_top":64,"padding_bottom":64,"padding_top_mob":48,"padding_bottom_mob":48}},"multi_column_wixBk6":{"type":"multi-column","blocks":{"item_EnEFWw":{"type":"item","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Watch_On_Youtube.jpg","column_size":"3","title":"","heading_tag":"h5","content":"","link_url":"","link_text":"Watch On Youtube","link_style":"button"}},"item_DTkmcC":{"type":"item","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Read_installation_guide.jpg","column_size":"3","title":"","heading_tag":"h4","content":"","link_url":"","link_text":"Read Installation Guide","link_style":"button"}},"item_a7jV8x":{"type":"item","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Lifestyle_Image.jpg","column_size":"3","title":"","heading_tag":"h4","content":"","link_url":"","link_text":"","link_style":"link"}}},"block_order":["item_EnEFWw","item_DTkmcC","item_a7jV8x"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"section_id":"installation_guide","full_width":true,"stack_on_mobile":false,"gap":"medium","text_alignment":"center","subheading":"","title":"Installation Guide","content":"<p